These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, social-worker
2 different games are played: poker, canasta
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, amber
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, train
House: ranch-style, palace
1. the owner of the goldfish is the person who likes amber##1
2. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
3. the videographer is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
6. the ranch-style house is not to the left of the person driving the train##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |
| Job      | social-worker      | videographer |
| Game          | canasta      | poker       |
| Pet         | frog | goldfish  |
| Color   | aquamarine     | amber      |
| Transport   | car       | train      |
| House         | palace    | ranch-style       |

