2. the mexican is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
4. the townhouse house is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
5. the german is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8
6. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre          | epic | sports |
| Birthday         | october  | september  |
| Nationality           | german      | mexican  |
| Beverage   | 7up     | almond-milk      |
| Sport           | rugby     | skiing    |
| House     | colonial  | townhouse     |

